@startuml

actor User
participant ":Ledger67" as App
participant ":Storage" as Storage
participant ":TransactionsList" as List
participant ":Transaction" as Transaction

== Application Startup ==
App -> Storage : new Storage("data/ledger.txt")
activate Storage
Storage --> App : storage instance
deactivate Storage

App -> List : new TransactionsList(Storage)
activate List
List -> Storage : load()
Storage --> List : List<Transaction>
deactivate List

== Add Transaction ==
User -> App : add command
App -> Transaction : new Transaction(...)
activate Transaction
Transaction --> App : transaction
deactivate Transaction

App -> List : addTransaction(transaction)
activate List
List -> Storage : save(transactions)
Storage --> List : success
List --> App : success
deactivate List

note over Storage
Persists transactions to file.
Loads on startup and saves after updates.
end note

@enduml
